    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are all at required level 1, consistent with the MRL 2 scope defined in ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. The CFD model is accepted as sufficiently credible to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 criterion is met across all five evaluated operating points.",
